{"tid":2505022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男學生涉旺角堵路受審  警: 只有示威者看到警方執法才會害怕及逃走","createTime":"2021-04-26T10:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T10:43:02.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a234d91e961a95f33b57db7b3a356f7a839be6c6","tid":2505022,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:06:43.000Z","msg":"去年5月27日有市民發起反對國歌法示威，警方當日拘捕逾百人，當中一名男學生被指在旺角呼籲示威者堵路。涉案男生否認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，今日受審。警員供稱，事發時被告站在示威人群前方，大叫：「手足！前面有狗呀！快啲丟啲垃圾出馬路，塞住啲黑警！」惟警員在盤問下同意，被告大叫後，其他示威者只是「想」撿起地上物品，<span class=\"red\">實際上並沒撿起</span>。辯方指被告當時正在過馬路，<span class=\"red\">「有狗呀」一語實是其身後的示威者所說</span>。案件押後至下月21日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n辯方播放被告遭制服時的片段，指畫面中不見路上有垃圾袋或雜物，鄧同意。鄧亦承認，他的三份書面供詞均沒提及搜查被告背包一事。<br />\n<br />\n徐在盤問下同意，當日情況混亂，現場有示威者、途人及街坊，有可能「撈亂」隨身物品。他強調被告有嫌疑，<span class=\"red\">因只有示威者看到警方執法才會害怕及逃走</span>，普通市民則會「若無其事企定定」。"},{"pid":"54a43fef00e417e4f11b8d2cf82f7e79d034e19b","tid":2505022,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/7IIVSELLGJCJLBDWN7LYACJ5J4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2F7IIVSELLGJCJLBDWN7LYACJ5J4%2F&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B65Urr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=b5d89981\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210426%2F7IIVSELLGJCJLBDWN7LYACJ5J4%2F&h=9f2a8eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210426/7IIVSELLGJCJLBDWN7LYACJ5J4/</a>"},{"pid":"38faf0efa352e236bfa7de74dd0a1c27ead6e4e2","tid":2505022,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21a5a26d9c59ec5f6c587162d42dfd846fa8d98","tid":2505022,"uid":21545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,